T02TD3592E:219a-1: dhva dz'a gra ke y'u r'a s'a dha nam /
T02TD3592E:219a-3: rgyal mtshan rtse mo'i dpung rgyan gyi sgrub thabs /
T02TD3592E:219a-4: rgyal mtshan rtse mo'i dpung rgyan la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02TD3592E:219a-5: rgyal mtshan rtse mo'i dpung rgyan sku mdog nag mo /
T02TD3592E:219a-8: dmar po dang ljang gu ni g-yas dang g-yon gyi zhal lo //
T02TD3592E:219a-9: phyag g-yas pa gnyis na ral gri dang /
T02TD3592E:219a-11: rdo rjes mtshan pa'i kha t'am ga dang /
T02TD3592E:219a-12: 'khor lo dag phyag g-yon pa dag na bsnams pa'o //
T02TD3592E:219a-13: dbu skra kham pa gyen du brdzes pa /
T02TD3592E:219a-14: thod pa skam po lngas dbu brgyan pa /
T02TD3592E:219a-15: stag gi bags pa'i sham thabs can /
T02TD3592E:219a-16: zhal mche ba gtsigs shing lto 'phyang ba /
T02TD3592E:219a-17: nyi ma'i gdan la zhabs g-yon brkyang gis bzhugs pa /
T02TD3592E:219a-20: sa bon ni h'um yig go //
T02TD3592E:219a-21: mi bskyod pas dbu brgyan pa can no //
T02TD3592E:219a-22: rgyal mtshan rtse mo'i dpung rgyan gyi sgrub thabs rdzogs so//
